quunwiner. Cover pet and bring to a rolling
boil. ece the lobters headfiest ino the pot and
covgf. When water retams to a boil, time cocking

TOSTEAM: Line a large ketile or stockpet with
od seaweed, if seaweed is not available,

TO SERVE Use a sarp, sturdy knife

from body and cack. Serve with
wam butter
